entities.VidPlayer/VidPlayerEntity.placements.name.vidPlayerEntity=In-Game Video Player
entities.VidPlayer/VidPlayerEntity.attributes.description.video=The OGV video source to play, formated as "ModName:/absolute/path/to/file.ogv".
entities.VidPlayer/VidPlayerEntity.attributes.description.muted=Whether the video's audio plays or not.
