entities.VidPlayer/VidPlayerEntity.attributes.description.hires=When false the video will be downscaled to pixel-art form.
entities.VidPlayer/VidPlayerEntity.attributes.description.volumeMult=Multiplier of the volume.
entities.VidPlayer/VidPlayerEntity.attributes.description.globalAlpha=Determines the Alpha value for the entire player (0 is fully transparent, 1 is fully opaque).
entities.VidPlayer/VidPlayerEntity.attributes.description.centered=Centers the video when keepAspectRatio is true.
entities.VidPlayer/VidPlayerEntity.attributes.description.chromaKey=Chroma Key color, leave empty to disable,
entities.VidPlayer/VidPlayerEntity.attributes.name.chromaKeyBaseThr=Chroma Key Base Threshold
entities.VidPlayer/VidPlayerEntity.attributes.description.chromaKeyBaseThr=Base threshold for Chroma Key, pixels below this threshold will be completely removed.
entities.VidPlayer/VidPlayerEntity.attributes.name.chromaKeyAlphaCorr=Chroma Key Alpha Correction
entities.VidPlayer/VidPlayerEntity.attributes.description.chromaKeyAlphaCorr=Alpha correction threshold, pixels below this threshold (starting from the Base threshold) will become proportionally transparent.
entities.VidPlayer/VidPlayerEntity.attributes.name.chromaKeySpill=Chroma Key Spill
entities.VidPlayer/VidPlayerEntity.attributes.description.chromaKeySpill=Color desaturation threshold, pixels below this threshold (starting from the Base threshold) will be proportionally desaturated.

